data.description: Unbelievable Vacaville location minutes from Travis Air Force Base, in the coveted Meadowlands! No rear neighbors, and a large lot. This four bedroom home offers high ceilings, two living rooms, a separated primary bedroom complete with bath and a beautiful back porch. Newer AC and Heating too! It's just awaiting your personal touch! A listing at this price is too good to last!
